description: Lists the problems with your application.

nested_items.name: ProblemList
nested_items.description: The list of problems.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The ID of the problem.

nested_items.name: Title
nested_items.description: The name of the problem.

nested_items.name: ShortName
nested_items.description: The short name of the problem associated with the SNS notification.

nested_items.name: Insights
nested_items.description: A detailed analysis of the problem using machine learning.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the problem.

nested_items.name: AffectedResource
nested_items.description: The resource affected by the problem.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time when the problem started, in epoch seconds.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The time when the problem ended, in epoch seconds.

nested_items.name: SeverityLevel
nested_items.description: A measure of the level of impact of the problem.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID for the owner of the resource group affected by the problem.

nested_items.name: ResourceGroupName
nested_items.description: The name of the resource group affected by the problem.
(string) ---
(string) ---

nested_items.name: RecurringCount
nested_items.description: The number of times that the same problem reoccurred after the first time it was resolved.

nested_items.name: LastRecurrenceTime
nested_items.description: The last time that the problem reoccurred after its last resolution.

nested_items.name: Visibility
nested_items.description: Specifies whether or not you can view the problem. Updates to ignored problems do not generate notifications.

nested_items.name: ResolutionMethod
nested_items.description: Specifies how the problem was resolved. If the value is AUTOMATIC, the system resolved the problem. If the value is MANUAL, the user resolved the problem. If the value is UNRESOLVED, then the problem is not resolved.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token used to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: ResourceGroupName
nested_items.description: The name of the resource group.

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID for the resource group owner.
